---

<MainLayout title="Alexis Vielma">
	<Stack slot="title" space="0.75rem">
		<h2 class="fs:md">
			<abbr title="Software Engineering">SWE</abbr> Intern @ <a href="https://lightbulb.ai">Lightbulb.ai</a>
		</h2>
		<p class="about">I design and build accessible and inclusive experiences for the web.</p>
	</Stack>
	<Stack space="var(--s4)">
		<Stack as="section" space="var(--s2)">
			<h3 class="fs:xs">About Me</h3>
			<p>
				I am an aspiring Software/Production Engineer who enjoys tackling technical challenges: be it <strong
					>code optimization</strong
				>, service management, or being able to interact with people outside of the industry. I have <strong
					>ever-growing technical skills</strong
				> and an <strong>on-going academic background</strong> in <abbr title="">Computer Science</abbr>, <abbr
					title="">Linguistics</abbr
				>, and <abbr title="">Korean</abbr>.
			</p>
			<p>
				My passion lies in being able to create fun and easy-to-use software that has the potential of reaching
				and helping many people while focusing on ease-of-use comes strong emphasis on <strong>UI/UX</strong>, <strong
					>HCI</strong
				>, and <strong>Continuous Development</strong>.
			</p>
			<p>
				I'm <strong>graduating in May 2025</strong> – Interested in Internship and Fellowship opportunities to further
				guide me in my career.
			</p>
		</Stack>
		<Stack as="section" space="var(--s2)">
			<h3 class="fs:xs">Experience</h3>
			<Stack space="var(--s3)">
				{jobs.map((job) => <JobExperience {...job} />)}
			</Stack>
			<div class="repel">
				<div></div>
				<a href="/resume" class="btn">View Resume</a>
			</div>
		</Stack>
		<Stack as="section" space="var(--s2)">
			<h3 class="fs:xs">Projects</h3>
			<div class="grid">
				<Project />
				<Project />
				<Project />
				<Project />
			</div>
		</Stack>
	</Stack>
</MainLayout>

<style>
	.about {
		max-width: 35ch;
	}

	h3 {
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}

	h3::before {
		content: "";
		display: inline-block;
		vertical-align: middle;
		margin-right: 1rem;
		width: 3rem;
		height: 0.075rem;
		background-color: black;
	}

	section p {
		margin: 0.5rem 0;
		font-size: 1rem;
	}
</style>
